*Clone and edit*
```bash
git clone https://github.com/ctwhome/dashboard.git
cd ./dashboard
yarn
yarn start
open: http://localhost:8080
```

## Development Process
As a designer and developer I enjoyed working on the assignment very much. I have created a modular React application based on components to approach the assignment. I have also created a mock data API to simulate data retrieving and an interactive PieChart. I have been sure that the website is fully responsive using Flexbox and CSS Modules. 

I hope this assigment fulfill the requirements for the job position. 

