### Swipe sidebar
A missing feature from the DeGiro mobile app is a native/like sidebar draggable effect. 
Please check my project from your phone to demo the effect https://goo.gl/QDEFMA

### My financial application: Valorlist
I'd like to share with you my financial application that i have made during my spear time from scratch. From the Analisys server to the design and development of the application. Made with Angular 1.5 (Components) and Angular material, and currently being moved the client to React.
Please check the video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Drg5Em0LVXY

